name.k: 元素図鑑 作・Theodore Gray
神奇的化学元素 – Theodore Gray

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Ever pondered the atomic weight of Bismuth? Do you debate the density of Niobium over dinner? If so, this app is for you. Chemistry truly comes to life with this fully interactive version of the periodic table. Engage with the elements like never before and witness the wonders of science in beautiful detail.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Chemistry comes to life with this interactive version of the periodic table.
